news.title: CCI orders probe into market abuse charges against Asian Paints
news.para: The direction follows a complaint filed by Grasim Industries (Birla Paints Division), which accused Asian Paints of engaging in exclusionary practices aimed at stifling its entry and growth in the Indian decorative paints segment.

news.title: NTT seeks up to $864 million in data centre REIT's Singapore IPO
news.para: NTT DC REIT's portfolio comprises six data centre assets located in the United States, Austria and Singapore, according to a preliminary prospectus filed on Friday.

news.title: ED raids Raheja Developers in case related to 'fraud' with homebuyers
news.para: The money laundering case of the Enforcement Directorate (ED) stems from multiple FIRs registered by the Economic Offences Wing (EOW) of the Delhi Police against Raheja Developers Ltd, its Managing Director Naveen Raheja and others, the federal agency said in a statement.
